      "id": "PopularPost262503",
      "post_content": "Sure, it's quite a bit of mana if you think about it, but look at it like this: You split it between three turns, you do it at instant speed, and you should only do it with leftover mana. It's a mana sink that turns into a Hellion. There's nothing wrong with that.  \n  \nPlus, have you seen the art? The art justifies the card.",
